JS MINIFIER: https://jscompress.com

CSS MINIFICATION:
Compress css file(combines multiple css into single css) - https://www.giftofspeed.com/css-compressor/
    Upload css files to above url and click on compress buton.
    Copy the transformed css from compressed output tab and paste it in corresponding styleBundle file
    
    Note: After copying in visual studio, if css looks formatted (with spaces and line breaks). Then, we have to turnoff formatOnPaste option to off.
    Follow the below steps to do the same:
      Tools -> Options -> Text Editor -> CSS -> Advanced.   In right side of window, under formatting dropdown, there will be "Format On Paste" dropdown, choose "Off" option from it.
    
